{"id":"3de6891abe822ce12a2f0f08e029cef1e6beb8f7","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1228459","title":"用 claude 桌面编程 和 cli 编程 有啥大的区别呢？ 不都是自动化的吗","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"V2EX (创意工作者社区)","byline":"blackantt","excerpt":"Claude - @blackantt - 没用过 claude 。 claude 桌面版 是否跟 chatgpt work 这种桌面端差不多，都能自动分析，操作/修改本地项目代码？","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div>\n    <div><P><a href=\"/tag/编程\"><li></li> 编程</a><a href=\"/tag/自动化\"><li></li> 自动化</a><a href=\"/tag/界面\"><li></li> 界面</a></P><p><span>17 replies &#160;<strong>•</strong> &#160;2026-07-20 18:34:57 +08:00</span>\n    </p></div>\n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881909\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8d13/4c44/631792_normal.png?m=1784253769\" alt=\"sentinelK\" data-uid=\"631792\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>2</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/sentinelK\">sentinelK</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 09:35:43 +08:00\">23h 3m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <div><p>这个没人能回复你，Claude 整个产品线都不开源。</p><p>OpenCode 是一致的，底层引擎的版本号都同步。</p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881960\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6239/84d7/459132_normal.png?m=1752839109\" alt=\"qW7bo2FbzbC0\" data-uid=\"459132\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>4</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/qW7bo2FbzbC0\">qW7bo2FbzbC0</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 09:41:53 +08:00\">22h 56m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>claude 桌面版用起来比 claude cli 方便多了，而且部分 code 会话可以跨端同步，更不用说 computer use 这些功能了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881979\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c3e79a09240ebb0f1c91510cfb9d5f7e?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"holmesx\" data-uid=\"608980\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>6</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/holmesx\">holmesx</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 09:44:16 +08:00\">22h 54m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>cli 的对话内容不随账号走，会本地记录。 没用过桌面版，桌面版的聊天内容是随账号走，还是本地记录呀？</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17882181\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b36b/3df5/748865_normal.png?m=1749550471\" alt=\"GopFei\" data-uid=\"748865\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>9</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/GopFei\">GopFei</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 10:11:55 +08:00\">22h 26m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>我用 cli 只是为了在 vs code ，以及其他工具里面用，不用一直切桌面。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17883173\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5129/e8be/40195_normal.png?m=1783687791\" alt=\"BeijingBaby\" data-uid=\"40195\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>11</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/BeijingBaby\">BeijingBaby</a></strong> &#160; <div><p>PRO</p></div>&#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 12:47:59 +08:00\">19h 50m ago via iPhone</span> \n                    \n                    <p>底层模型一致，体验差别，桌面版图形界面，cli 可以通过命令行调用 更好做自动化之类的操作</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17883899\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e956/45ce/233781_normal.png?m=1779448642\" alt=\"rayyume\" data-uid=\"233781\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>12</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/rayyume\">rayyume</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 15:03:16 +08:00\">17h 35m ago via Android</span> \n                    \n                    <p>家里服务器部署 code-server+hapi 调用模型，用的是真爽，都不用考虑多端同步了，直接公网访问 pwa 就能随时随地用了。只不过 claude code 掉登录有点频繁，codex 很持久。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17885416\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dbc9/1eaf/89635_normal.png?m=1776671720\" alt=\"EthanZC\" data-uid=\"89635\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>17</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/EthanZC\">EthanZC</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 18:34:57 +08:00\">14h 3m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>Claude 桌面客户端,写代码,就是启动 Claude Code 来执行的</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n</div></DIV>","content_text"